  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Counts-per-Unit</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true"> :the number of encoder counts per </text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; color:#000000;" translate="true">mm </text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">(or other unit, as defined in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Y-Units" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#800000;" translate="true">Y–axis Units</link><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#800000;" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text - small" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Body Text - small" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">For example: if a servomotor has an encoder resolution of 1024 counts per revolution, driving a 5:1 gearbox, with a 40 tooth pulley mounted on the gearbox shaft, with each tooth having a 5mm pitch, then the counts per mm would be:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Text - small" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none; font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Body Text - small" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Body Text - small" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">40*(T/pulley rev) * 5(mm/T) = 200 mm/pulley rev...</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Body Text - small" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Body Text - small" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">1024(Counts/motor rev) * 5(motor rev/pulley rev) = 5120 counts/pulley rev...</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Body Text - small" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Body Text - small" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">5120 (counts/pulley rev) / 200 (mm/pulley rev) = 25.6 counts per mm.</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
